90
00:07:01,370 --> 00:07:05,500
I heard you took charge of a subsidiary right after graduating college.

91
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:07,380
Yes.

92
00:07:08,010 --> 00:07:12,900
Back then, I was also courageous like you guys.

93
