No, I don't.

135
00:09:14,540 --> 00:09:16,730
- Come on, show me just once.
- I don't have one.

136
00:09:16,730 --> 00:09:18,340
Show us now! President Kim!

137
00:09:18,340 --> 00:09:19,950
Show us now!

138
00:09:19,950 --> 00:09:21,610
Show us now!

