150
00:10:19,190 --> 00:10:22,540
We have to hurry to be on time.

151
00:10:25,790 --> 00:10:28,140
Oh, there he comes.

152
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:41,060
I haven't seen him before.

153
00:10:42,650 --> 00:10:44,100
I forgot the introductions.

154
00:10:44,100 --> 00:10:47,860
I hired him as my bodyguard and personal driver.

155
00:10:47,860 --> 00:10:50,970
- Oh, did you, really?
- Yes.

156
00:10:54,230 --> 00:10:57,020
If you had let me know, I would've found a better

157
00:10:57,020 --> 00:10:59,500
person for you!

158
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,980
Hey, you asshole, are you in that much of a rush?

159
00:11:06,980 --> 00:11:09,770
Do you want me to send you on an express trip to the afterlife?

160
00:11:15,580 --> 00:11:18,580
Where did Secretary Jeong go for a person like him to be here instead?

161
00:11:19,710 --> 00:11:21,700
I had something for her to do. Hold on tight.

162
00:11:21,700 --> 00:11:24,290
Yes. I'm– Aigoo!

163
00:11:24,290 --> 00:11:27,180
Of course, I know Mr. Nam from the Sales Department.

164
00:11:27,180 --> 00:11:30,100
