189
00:12:57,930 --> 00:12:59,800
I mean,

190
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:03,740
a corporation needs to make money. Why do you need a domed stadium?

191
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:05,510
Let her be.

192
00:13:05,510 --> 00:13:09,040
It'll be my niece's decisive mistake.

193
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:15,960
I'd like to disclose another teaching left behind by the previous chairman.

194
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:18,070
President Park In Seong!

195
00:13:19,250 --> 00:13:21,460
Please join me up here for a moment.

196
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:37,610
Level Four Self-Driving Cars, collaborated by Beomyeong Auto and Silver Lining,

197
00:13:37,610 --> 00:13:42,030
