199
00:13:51,270 --> 00:13:53,440
I apologize.

200
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:54,730
It's not ready yet.

201
00:13:54,730 --> 00:13:57,610
Just launch it by National Foundation Day.

202
00:13:57,610 --> 00:14:00,540
I'll take care of the rest.

203
00:14:06,740 --> 00:14:09,470
He showed up after two months here.

204
00:14:14,110 --> 00:14:16,390
He showed up after three months at different times.

205
00:14:16,390 --> 00:14:22,490
Gosh, at this rate, we can't figure out why Mr. Nam went to the hiking club.

206
00:14:22,490 --> 00:14:24,380
Not at all.

207
00:14:24,380 --> 00:14:28,370
There is a rule between those dates.

208
00:14:28,370 --> 00:14:34,430
Executive Director Oh is trying to gain an advantage in the share fight by hurriedly launching the self-driving car

209
00:14:34,430 --> 00:14:38,040
- before the end-of-the-year meeting.
- Who doesn't know that?

210
00:14:38,040 --> 00:14:39,610
My apologies.

211
00:14:39,610 --> 00:14:43,490
Even in President Kim Seon Ju's absence,

212
00:14:43,490 --> 00:14:47,910
