213
00:14:48,820 --> 00:14:50,980
There is no way.

214
00:14:50,980 --> 00:14:54,800
[Attendance Sheet]

215
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:56,710
What's the rule?

216
00:14:56,710 --> 00:15:01,840
