255
00:18:06,950 --> 00:18:11,940
I was lonely during the weekend, so I only attended a few meetings.

256
00:18:13,350 --> 00:18:15,130
By the way, though,

257
00:18:15,130 --> 00:18:22,280
Mr. Nam coincidentally attended the hiking club only when you attended as well, Director Kwak.

258
00:18:22,280 --> 00:18:24,600
I'm not sure.

259
00:18:24,600 --> 00:18:27,510
I don't even know the dates

260
00:18:27,510 --> 00:18:29,740
